column5: Well I leave in 37 days for my annual trip to Gull Rock. Was curious on if anyone had been there yet and how the fishing was?

I would refer to this post for current reports and what not.https://www.walleyecentral.com/forums...=181003&page=5Fishing started off slow for everyone sounded like but last few weeks it has picked up! We are headed up in 10 days and crossing our fingers fishing shall be AWESOME.
